    <name>NoLimitConnect</name>
    <summary>Decentralized social networking and messaging platform</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            NoLimitConnect is a full-featured independent social networking platform
            designed to be hosted on any device with an internet connection.
        </p>
        <p>
            It provides messaging, voice and video communication, media sharing,
            blogging, and real-time collaboration tools without relying on centralized
            services.
        </p>
        <p>
            Visit https://nolimitconnect.org for full details and documentation.
        </p>
    </description>

    <categories>
        <category>Network</category>
        <category>Chat</category>
